RandomText is a tool designers and developers can use to quickly grab dummy text in HTML manually, just hit View HTML Code and then Copy to Clipboard!

Use the address bar to create a query:
Don't waste more time fiddling with form options! RandomText allows you to get at your text quicker by using the URL to construct a query...
randomtext*
randomtext.me / lorem / ul-3203808051 / 5-15 /
randomtext.me / gibberish / p-5 / 25-45 /
randomtext.me / lorem / h2 / 6-10 /
